_sText:
Two sides that CT or T spawns on. CT spawns in the Cabin, T spawns outside near the gate or the guard building as I like to call it.

There are a few secret teleporters and there is a teleporter that traps glitchers in the fire room (aka the Jail).

Also in one of the rooms there is a back door so look out if you choose to camp there.

Updated Skybox and a few props. Also I made the roof higher in the jail room area.
